test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (6 == 3)
 +  where 6 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x73c1b8071ac0>([42])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x73c1b8071ac0> = [[1, 42], [42], [1, 42, 1], [42], [42, 1], [1, 42], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 1 == 42
 +  where 1 = <built-in function prod>([])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
